#   intended to run in multiple environments; otherwise, check them in:
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1185, it is recommended to check Pipfile.lock into git.
#   However, in case of a library/package, you might want to ignore it.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is generally recommended to check poetry.lock into git.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is generally recommended to check pdm.lock into git.
